msgctxt "5705"
msgid ""
"はぁ……　はぁ……\n"
"どうだった……？"
msgstr "Hmm ... Hmm ... How was it ...?"

msgctxt "5742"
msgid ""
"素晴らしいですわっ！\n"
"やはり、私の目に狂いはなかった！\n"
"華のある、良い踊りでしたわよ！"
msgstr ""
"It's wonderful! After all, there was nothing wrong with my eyes! It was a "
"brilliant and good dance!"

msgctxt "5829"
msgid ""
"はぁ……　はぁ……\n"
"どうだった……？"
msgstr "Hmm ... Hmm ... How was it ...?"

msgctxt "5866"
msgid ""
"まだまだ荒削りですが、初めてとしては上出来ですわ！\n"
"やはり……　私の目に狂いはなかったですわ！"
msgstr ""
"It's still rough, but it's good for the first time! After all ... I didn't "
"go crazy in my eyes!"

msgctxt "5961"
msgid ""
"そうか……　ならよかった。\n"
"なかなか奥が深いものだな。"
msgstr "I see ... I wish I had. It's quite deep."

msgctxt "6016"
msgid ""
"そうなのですわ。まぁそこが、面白いところでも\n"
"あるんですけれどね。"
msgstr "That's right. Well, that's also an interesting place."

msgctxt "6083"
msgid ""
"もし気に入っていただけたなら……\n"
"またいらしてください。\n"
"斎藤さんには、特別価格で教えて差し上げますわ。"
msgstr ""
"If you like it ... please come again. I will tell Mr. Saito at a special "
"price."

msgctxt "6188"
msgid "ふっ……　なんだ、結局店への勧誘だったのか？"
msgstr "Hmm ... What was it, after all, a solicitation to the store?"

msgctxt "6233"
msgid ""
"おほほほ。\n"
"いつの時代も、体験授業というものは顧客獲得と\n"
"密接に関係しているものですわ。"
msgstr ""
"Cheeks. Experience-based lessons have always been closely related to "
"customer acquisition."

msgctxt "6322"
msgid "商売上手だな。まったく……"
msgstr "You're a business person. Jeez……"

msgctxt "6349"
msgid ""
"まぁ、それは冗談として……\n"
"斎藤さんには見込みがあるのは事実ですわ。"
msgstr ""
"Well, that's a joke ... It's true that Mr. Saito has a lot of potential."

msgctxt "6418"
msgid ""
"気分転換にもなりますし、お暇なときにでもぜひ。\n"
"いつでもお待ちしておりますわ。"
msgstr ""
"It's a refreshing experience, and even when you're free. We are always "
"waiting for you."

msgctxt "6497"
msgid ""
"ああ。気が向いたら顔を出すとする。\n"
"じゃあな、舞城……　先生。"
msgstr ""
"Oh. Suppose you show your face when you feel like it. Well then, Maijo ... "
"Sensei."

msgctxt "6560"
msgid "ええ。それでは。お待ちしてますわ。"
msgstr "Yeah. Well then. I'll be waiting for you."

msgctxt "6595"
msgid ""
"（舞踊、か……\n"
"　確かに奥が深いし、面白いものだな。\n"
"　暇があったら、また顔を出してみるか……）"
msgstr ""
"(Dance, or ... It's certainly deep and interesting. If I have time, I'll "
"come back again ...)"

msgctxt "6697"
msgid ""
"ここが「にちぶ座」か……\n"
"趣のある、良い内装だな。"
msgstr "Is this \"Nichibu-za\" ... It's a nice and quaint interior."

msgctxt "6748"
msgid ""
"ほほほ。そうでしょ？\n"
"さて、それではこれからみっちりと、\n"
"基礎を教えますからね。覚悟してくださいな。"
msgstr ""
"Cheeks. Right? Well then, I will teach you the basics exactly from now on. "
"Please be prepared."

msgctxt "6849"
msgid "う、うむ……"
msgstr "Umm ..."

msgctxt "6862"
msgid "日本舞踊　その弐へ進む。"
msgstr "Go to the second Japanese dance."

msgctxt "6888"
msgid "日本舞踊　説明終了。"
msgstr "The explanation of Japanese dance is over."

msgctxt "6910"
msgid "もう一度、遊び方を確認しますか？"
msgstr "Would you like to see how to play again?"

msgctxt "6943"
msgid "う～む……　なるほどな。"
msgstr "Hmm ... I see."

msgctxt "6968"
msgid ""
"……さぁ、これで一通り基礎は教えましたわ。\n"
"あとは、実践してみましょう。"
msgstr "...... Now, I've taught you the basics. After that, let's practice."

msgctxt "7041"
msgid "実践？"
msgstr "Practice?"

msgctxt "7048"
msgid ""
"ええ。今から曲を流しますので、\n"
"それに合わせて踊ってみてくださいな。"
msgstr "Yeah. I'm going to play a song from now on, so please dance to it."

msgctxt "7117"
msgid "い、いきなりか？"
msgstr "Suddenly?"

msgctxt "7134"
msgid ""
"習うより慣れろ、がうちの教室の方針なんです。\n"
"では、いきますわよ！"
msgstr ""
"It's our classroom policy to get used to it rather than learn it. Let's go!"

